title: Vicki Chase Cuckold
description: Placed yourself in Jerome's shoes: you get a distraught call from your better half and surge home to be close by just to find that her weeps for help come down to encouraging her wanton ways. If you were in Jerome's shoes, you'd be sniffing the tip of an interesting man's instrument just to see your better half grin. Would you isn't that right? In light of the grin all over, it is by all accounts the way to a cheerful marriage (at any rate for her!)
